  "headline": "Transfer Learning",
  "description": "Transfer learning applies knowledge from a source domain to improve learning in a target domain. In deep learning: pre-train on large generic dataset (ImageNet), fine-tune on specific task with small labeled dataset. This is the dominant paradigm in computer vision and NLP — training from scratch is rare.",
